USAGE

1. Install script on page within the <body>

2. Set the element with id=show1 you want to hide as display:none; (It does not need to be a div)

3. Manilulate the url to show the content

 - VALID: https://www.example.com/?show1
 - VALID: https://www.example.com/?show2
 - VALID: https://www.example.com/?show1show2
 - INVALID: https://www.example.com/?show12 (unless you have defined show12 as a seperate id to show)
